===Genetic screening===
The ability to upregulate gene expression using dCas9-SunTag with a single sgRNA also opens the door to large-scale genetic screens, such as [[Perturb-seq]], to uncover phenotypes that result from increased or decreased gene expression, which will be especially important for understanding the effects of gene regulation in cancer.<ref name=""pmid25307933"">{{Cite journal
 | pmid = 25307933
| pmc = 4252608
| year = 2014
