* 2016 – [[New York University]] (NYU)<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.nyu.edu/about/news-publications/news/2016/march/darren-walker-ford-foundation-president-to-speak-at-nyus-commencement.html|title=Darren Walker, Ford Foundation President, to Speak at NYU's Commencement|website=nyu.edu}}</ref>
