* 2017 – [[Hong Kong University of Science and Technology]]<ref>[http://www.ust.hk/about-hkust/media-relations/press-releases/hkust-holds-25th-congregation-conferring-honorary-doctorates-four-distinguished-academics-community-leaders/ HKUST Holds 25th Congregation Conferring Honorary Doctorates on  Four Distinguished Academics and Community Leaders], retrieved 20 November 2017</ref>
