* 2018 – [[University of Manchester]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.manchester.ac.uk/discover/news/businessman-scientists-actor-and-architect-university-foundation-day/|title=Businessman, scientists, actor and architect honoured as University marks its Foundation Day|website=manchester.ac.uk}}</ref>
* 2019 – [[McGill University]], Canada<ref>{{cite web |date=16 April 2019 |title=McGill's Honorary Degree recipients for Spring Convocation 2019 |url=https://www.mcgill.ca/newsroom/channels/news/mcgills-honorary-degree-recipients-spring-convocation-2019-296322 |work=mcgill.ca |location=Montreal |publisher=McGill University |access-date=18 June 2020}}</ref>

