In 1971, [[Clyde Hutchison]] and Marshall Edgell showed that it is possible to produce mutants with small fragments of [[Phi X 174|phage ϕX174]] and [[restriction nuclease]]s.<ref>{{Cite journal 
| last1 = Hutchison Ca | first1 = 3. 
