| first9 = Edwin
| date = 2013-12-05
| title = Functional repair of CFTR by CRISPR/Cas9 in intestinal stem cell organoids of cystic fibrosis patients
| journal = Cell Stem Cell
| volume = 13
| issue = 6
| pages = 653–658
| doi = 10.1016/j.stem.2013.11.002
| issn = 1875-9777
| pmid = 24315439
| doi-access = free
}}</ref> Subsequent applications built upon simple sequence corrections and successfully repaired a chromosomal inversion abnormality in [[Haemophilia A|Hemophilia A]].<ref>{{Cite journal
| last1 = Park
| first1 = Chul-Yong
| last2 = Kim
| first2 = Duk Hyoung
| last3 = Son
